[subsection [title Overview] [id pkg.orientation.overview]]
[paragraph]
The [term [type package] sombrero] package implements a modular
[link-ext [target "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GLSL"] GLSL] preprocessing
system. It provides a simple module system that allows for the publishing
and re-use of sets of shaders.

